        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At the crossroads of sport and fashion lies Greyson Clothiers, a brand that has redefined the very essence of golf apparel. Born from the vision of uniting fashion and sport, Greyson has become synonymous with functionality, innovation, and creativity. With the principles of the wolf at the helm, Founder and CEO Charlie Schaefer built a team founded on camaraderie, loyalty, strength, and community. By crafting products that can perform at the highest level through superior tailoring and construction, Greyson has shattered the idea that sport, tailored fashion, and functionality cannot coexist. In the pursuit to redefine modern menswear, Greyson welcomes all those who strive for greatness to run along with the Pack.</p>"
          }
        }
