            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The Pack calls on all individuals who know when to lead the Pack, when to be a team player, and carry the passion and desire to stand up for what they believe in – built on equal parts individuality and togetherness. The juxtaposition of technical performance and refined sophistication lies at the core of the brand DNA. Through the individuality of personal expression, the singularity of the sport, and the camaraderie that it forges, Greyson strives to engage with each individual who is as passionate about what they put on as much as they are passionate about what they use it for. Greyson breaks through the traditional rulebook of golf and tennis fashion; it is a brand that extends far beyond sport. Through clothing, Greyson has found a platform to impact communities, address adversity, and create space for all people to dream.</p>"
