            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Greyson Clothiers was born out of founder Charlie Schaefer's deep desire to create a brand of clothing that he would wear. Taking 13 years of design experience and the inspiration of a newly formed family of his own, Charlie set out to create a brand that would become a legacy to his children. Greyson, his first-born daughter, and Scarlett, his second-born daughter, are the inspirations for a brand that stands for something more, which can influence and change the future. Greyson is also worn by multiple PGA Tour athletes including Justin Thomas, Luke Donald, Erik Van Rooyen, Thorbjorn Olesen, Akshay Bhatia, Luke List & Sam Ryder.</p>"
          }
        }
