        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The latest Greyson collection offers bold printed/premium fabric polo shirts, cashmere hoodies, tailored shorts, as well as quarter zips/mid-layers, offering something for any occasion on the course with the best fabrics and unique prints. Each piece in the collection is crafted with the utmost attention to detail, ensuring both style and performance on the green.</p><p>• Polo Shirts: The bold printed/premium fabric polo shirts are designed to make a statement on and off the course. These polo shirts are more than just sportswear; they are a symbol of personal expression and individuality.</p><p>• Cashmere Hoodies: Luxurious and comfortable, the cashmere hoodies from Greyson Clothiers provide the perfect balance between style and functionality. Whether you're on the course or relaxing afterwards, these hoodies are a must-have in any golfer's wardrobe.</p><p>• Tailored Shorts: Greyson's tailored shorts are designed for the modern golfer. Made with the finest materials and crafted with precision, these shorts offer both style and functionality, allowing you to move freely and comfortably on the course.</p><p>• Quarter Zips/Mid-layers: The quarter zips/mid-layers from Greyson Clothiers are the perfect layering pieces for any golfer. Whether you need an extra layer of warmth on a cool day or simply want to add a touch of style to your outfit, these quarter zips/mid-layers have you covered.</p>"
          }
        }
